        <updateDate>2026-02-27T19:58:49Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[<p><strong>Bill to Outlaw Wounding of Official Working Animals Act or the BOWOW Act</strong></p><p>This bill establishes that a&nbsp;non-U.S. national (<em>alien</em> under federal law) convicted of, or who admits to having committed, an offense related to harming animals used in law enforcement is inadmissible and deportable.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
